    <briefdescription>
<para>Configuration for matrix multiplication operations. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhipdnn__frontend_1_1graph_1_1MatmulAttributes" kindref="compound">MatmulAttributes</ref> specifies the parameters for a matrix multiplication operation: C = A @ B. Supports batched operations when tensors have leading batch dimensions.</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Matrix<sp/>multiplication:<sp/>C<sp/>=<sp/>A<sp/>@<sp/>B</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
